the truth. the whole truth.

702
00:33:42.175 --> 00:33:44.052
and nothing but the truth?
-Yes.

703
00:33:44.175 --> 00:33:46.009
Have a seat.

704
00:33:54.246 --> 00:33:56.311
No. not in my courtroom.

705
00:33:56.395 --> 00:33:57.915
Jimmy. tell them they
can wait outside.

706
00:33:57.999 --> 00:34:00.293
but they are not welcome here.

707
00:34:13.638 --> 00:34:15.978
Mr. Ruíz. you did a great job.

708
00:34:16.062 --> 00:34:17.934
Couldn't have asked
for a better witness.

709
00:34:18.018 --> 00:34:21.230
Mr. Ruíz. put your
hands behind your back.

710
00:34:21.314 --> 00:34:23.692
You're under arrest.

711
00:34:24.113 --> 00:34:25.615
Okay. listen. they're
gonna take you

712
00:34:25.699 --> 00:34:27.117
